Steps to use the script: 
Open Notepad on the computer. 
Copy and paste the script in the notepad. 
Save the file on desktop as CP-Hardening.ps1. 
Open powershell as administrator. 
Copy the path for the file in file explorer. 
Type cd (Path for the file) to open the file directory.
Then open the file using this command: .\CP-Hardening.ps1. 
Then use the script :). 
Btw I did not use Ai to make this part. 